    A cat is a domesticated mammal of the Felis catus species.\n

    Cat or CAT may also refer to:\n

    \n
    \n

    Animals[edit]

    \n
    • Felidae (the cats or felids), a family of Carnivorans\n
      • Pantherinae (big cats), a subfamily
        • \n
      • Felinae (small cats), the other subfamily
    \n
